\c 10
\s Inzalo yamadodana kaNowa
\p
\v 1 Lezi-ke yizizukulwana zamadodana kaNowa: UShemu, uHamu loJafethi. Kwasekuzalwa amadodana kubo emva kukazamcolo.
\v 2 Amadodana kaJafethi\x + 1 Lan. 1.5-7.\x*: UGomeri\x + Hez. 38.6.\x* loMagogi\x + Hez. 38.2,3; 39.1.\x* loMadayi loJavani\x + Dan. 11.2.\x* loTubali loMesheki loTirasi.
\v 3 Lamadodana kaGomeri: UAshikenazi\x + Jer. 51.27.\x* loRifathi loTogarma\x + Hez. 38.6.\x*.
\v 4 Lamadodana kaJavani: UElisha loTarshishi\x + Hlab. 72.10. Hez. 38.13.\x*, amaKiti\x + Hlab. 72.10. Isa. 11.11; 40.15. Jer. 2.10; 25.22. Hez. 27.6. Zef. 2.11.\x* lamaDodani.
\v 5 Kwehlukaniswa kusukela kubo izihlenge\x + Hlab. 72.10. Isa. 11.11; 40.15. Jer. 2.10; 25.22. Hez. 27.6. Zef. 2.11.\x* zezizwe emazweni abo, ngulowo lalowo ngokolimi lwakhe, langokosendo lwabo, ezizweni zabo.
\p
\v 6 Lamadodana kaHamu\x + 1 Lan. 1.8-10.\x*: UKushi\x + Jer. 46.9.\x* loMizirayimi loPuti\x + Jer. 46.9.\x* loKhanani.
\v 7 Lamadodana kaKushi: USeba loHavila loSabitha loRama loSabitheka. Lamadodana kaRahama: UShebha\x + Hlab. 72.10. Hez. 38.13.\x* loDedani\x + Hlab. 72.10. Hez. 38.13.\x*.
\v 8 UKushi wasezala uNimrodi; yena waqala ukuba liqhawe emhlabeni.
\v 9 Yena waba ngumzingeli olamandla phambi kweN\sc KOSI\sc*; ngakho kuthiwa: NjengoNimrodi, umzingeli olamandla phambi kweN\sc KOSI\sc*.
\v 10 Lokuqala kombuso wakhe yiBabeli leEreki leAkadi leKaline elizweni leShinari\x + 11.2.\x*.
\v 11 Kwaphuma\f + \fk kaphuma: \fl kumbe, \fq waphuma waye eAsiriya.\f* kulelolizwe uAshuri, wasesakha iNinive leRehobothi-Ire leKala,
\v 12 leReseni phakathi kweNinive leKala; lo ngumuzi omkhulu.
\v 13 UMizirayimi wasezala\x + 1 Lan. 1.11-16.\x* amaLudi lamaAnami lamaLehabi lamaNafethuhi
\v 14 lamaPatrusi lamaKaseluhi - lapho okwavela khona amaFilisti\x + Jer. 47.4. Amos 9.7. Gen. 21. Dute. 2.23.\x* - lamaKafitori\x + Jer. 47.4. Amos 9.7. Gen. 21. Dute. 2.23.\x*.
\p
\v 15 UKhanani wasezala uSidoni\f + \fk uSidoni: \fl Heb. \fq uThizidoni.\f* izibulo lakhe, loHethi,
\v 16 lomJebusi lomAmori lomGirigashi
\v 17 lomHivi lomArki lomSini
\v 18 lomArvadi lomZemari lomHamathi; lemva kwalokho usendo lwamaKhanani lwahlakazeka.
\v 19 Umngcele wamaKhanani wasusukela eSidoni usiya eGerari uze ufike eGaza\f + \fk iGaza: \fl Heb. \fq iAza.\f*, usiya eSodoma leGomora leAdima leZeboyimi kuze kufike eLasha.
\v 20 La ngamadodana kaHamu, ngokosendo lwawo, langendimi zawo, emazweni awo, ezizweni zawo.
\p
\v 21 UShemu laye wasezalelwa amadodana; unguyise wamadodana wonke akaEberi, umfowabo kaJafethi, omkhulu.
\v 22 Amadodana kaShemu\x + 1 Lan. 1.17-25.\x*: UElamu loAshuri loArpakishadi loLudi loAramu.
\v 23 Lamadodana kaAramu\x + 1 Lan. 1.17.\x*: UUzi loHuli loGetheri loMashi.
\v 24 UArpakishadi wasezala uShela\x + 11.12.\x*; uShela wasezala uEberi.
\v 25 Kwasekuzalelwa uEberi amadodana amabili, ibizo lomunye nguPelegi\f + \fk uPelegi: \fl okuyikuthi, \fq ukwehlukana.\f*, ngoba ensukwini zayo umhlaba wehlukaniswa; lebizo lomfowabo nguJokithani.
\v 26 UJokithani wasezala uAlimodadi loShelefi loHazamavethi loJera
\v 27 loHadoramu loUzali loDikila
\v 28 loObali loAbhimayeli loShebha
\v 29 loOfiri\x + 1 Kho. 9.26-28; 10.11.\x* loHavila loJobabi; bonke labo ngamadodana kaJokithani.
\v 30 Indawo yokuhlala kwabo isukela eMesha lapho usiya eSefari, intaba yempumalanga.
\v 31 La ngamadodana kaShemu, ngokosendo lwabo langendimi zabo, emazweni abo ngokwezizwe zabo.
\p
\v 32 Lolu lusendo lwamadodana kaNowa ngezizukulwana zawo ezizweni zawo; kwasekusehlukaniswa kulaba izizwe emhlabeni emva kukazamcolo.
